snippet.title: Impossiball Gameplay Trailer 09 Dec 2016
snippet.description:
Raw gameplay footage of IMPOSSIBALL showing off the three main camera angles and some of the power-ups. The video was captured with FRAPS at 60 fps.
Buy Impossiball on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/374460/
